  "description": [
    "WASHINGTON GAS MAKESGOODGAIN Leads Local Market in ActivityTractions Nominal Three Calls a Year BY I A FLEMING Washington Gas was the feature of todays session After a prolonged period of more or less weakness with slow declines the stock turned strong opening at 56 and closing at 37 to 56 In all 143 shares were sold more than double the business of the last few weeks In the oldtime favorite Buyers and sellers could not get together In the first fifteen minutes of the session and it was not until i after the call that there was any rhing doing The street railways were entirely nominal After considerable Jockeying 564 was bid for the common with 7 asked while a sale of the preferred was made at 73 Capital Traction was 103 bid Mergenthaler advanced to 179 on moderate business Total business was largely restricted j Should Buy Governments i With the federal reserve banks not making more than enough to pay the j i per cent interest on their capital j stock to member banks with but 25 j per cent of the resources working it would seem that the time was ripe tor the employment of their funds"
